00:02:00.239 --> 00:02:04.480
So what we're going to talk about today is code promotion, which is generally sort of

00:02:05.120 --> 00:02:09.520
the sequence of things you want to do to put something into production in a way where it's

00:02:09.520 --> 00:02:10.080
protected, right?

00:02:10.080 --> 00:02:11.600
