00:02:11.600 --> 00:02:17.279
And that is being able to test, validate, and sort of make sure the thing is ready before

00:02:17.279 --> 00:02:17.919
it goes up.

00:02:17.919 --> 00:02:18.800
So that's part one.

00:02:18.800 --> 00:02:22.960
And then part two is making sure it only goes up once you've done those things, right?

00:02:22.960 --> 00:02:26.399
You have a validation plan, and it only goes there once it's validated.

00:02:27.839 --> 00:02:29.919
So I will say this is a little bit of an advanced maneuver.

00:02:30.880 --> 00:02:34.160
And so I would suggest you do some other stuff first.

00:02:34.160 --> 00:02:36.639
So writing good code is really helpful.

