And Mark, I think, talked a bunch about that and also had some of these similar resources.

00:02:41.520 --> 00:02:43.520
Doing some basic project hygiene, right?

00:02:43.520 --> 00:02:48.000
Using projects, using correctly subpath kind of things.

00:02:48.000 --> 00:02:53.199
If you know the What They Forgot to Teach You About R course, it's there.

00:02:53.199 --> 00:02:54.399
Using Git is good.

00:02:54.399 --> 00:02:57.759
